OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAnti-Semitism row: Royal   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FCourt Theatre apologises   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F'unreservedly'             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, London's Royal Court Theatre has       
OL,6, apologised "unreservedly" after hosting
OL,7, a play accused of perpetuating an      
OL,8, anti-Semitic stereotype.               
OL,10,FIn December, the theatre lost two      
OL,11,Ffinancial backers after putting on a   
OL,12,Fnew play, Rare Earth Mettle.           
OL,14,FThe row surrounded the role of Hershel 
OL,15,FFink, a manipulative billionaire who,  
OL,16,Fdespite his name, is not Jewish.       
OL,18,FOn Tuesday, the theatre admitted it    
OL,19,F"fell short" of its "ambitions in terms
OL,20,Fof inclusivity and anti-racism".       
